race.description: Ladbrokes Future Stars Series Heat 5 Maiden Plate
race.comment: KIPPIS (8) is knocking on the door and rates highly here. She was well backed last time at Warrnambool and just missed when going down by a neck, giving every indication the rise to 1200m would suit better. Melham goes aboard from a soft gate and she can get the job done. SHARE THE STARS (7) resumed with a solid run at Terang with a close-up fourth. She'll be fitter now and should take holding out again. MAHRAJAN (9) is a filly by Pride Of Dubai on debut for the Hayes yard. She's trialled well enough and should be ready to go from the inside gate. BLACK COAL (2) has had two runs this time in, improving last time out here when sticking on solidly for fourth. Peaks now and can take catching.
